psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher

Interface SourceEnricher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CvTermEnricher<Source>, MIEnricher<Source>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FullSourceEnricher, FullSourceUpdater, MinimalSourceEnricher, MinimalSourceUpdater

    public interface SourceEnricher
extends CvTermEnricher<Source>
    The source enricher is an enricher which can enrich either single source or a collection. A source enricher must be initiated with a fetcher. Sub- enrichers: publication enricher. Will not enrich the publication if the publication enricher is null
    Since:
    29/01/14
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Marine Dumousseau (marine@ebi.ac.uk)
